    "description": "Golf Rush is a golfing game where the goal is not to hit in the least strokes possible but instead by being the fastest golfer.<br>You race your friends in this multiplayer golf racing game!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Golfing</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/c26ff1aefdabeba9da58b2d48c016fb6.poster.avif?t=1722947793\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/c26ff1aefdabeba9da58b2d48c016fb6.webm?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/c26ff1aefdabeba9da58b2d48c016fb6.mp4?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You golf by timing both the direction of the shot and the power of the swing. <br>Watch out for aggressive competetors! They might smack you with their golf club...<br></li><li> <strong>Golfcart Drift Racing</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/642e338232ccbe03426c9c11369e0295.poster.avif?t=1722947793\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/642e338232ccbe03426c9c11369e0295.webm?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/642e338232ccbe03426c9c11369e0295.mp4?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To get to you ball you will need to be fast. The golfcart will help you do just that.<br>Thanks to the drifting boost mechanics you will be able to reach high speeds!<br></li><li> <strong>Powerups</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/e8b238312ade22d47f829d1cd5ec806d.poster.avif?t=1722947793\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/e8b238312ade22d47f829d1cd5ec806d.webm?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/e8b238312ade22d47f829d1cd5ec806d.mp4?t=1722947793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sometimes you need that extra edge in the competition. Use a collection of different powerups to help you win!<br></li><li> <strong>Obstacles</strong><br>There are a collection of obstacles that interact with you, your car or your ball. <br>The boost ramp which launches your car, The hoops that launch your ball, The bonus areas that give you extra points and many more map specific obstacles!<br></li><li> <strong>Rush Mode</strong><br>If you and your friends want an extra challenge you could try the Rush mode. Here all players share only one ball!<br>Score by hitting the ball as far as possible with a boost for the player that scores in the hole.  <br></li><li> <strong>Loads of maps!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083380/extras/005d2ca0c6ee46ae21ad108377c170f7.avif?t=1722947793\" width=600 height=400 /></span><br>With 4 unique maps there will never be a boring moment!</li></ul>",
